@902 = ~Amorphous Disciple~ 
@903 = ~AMORPHOUS DISCIPLE: The foul ichor of oozes runs through your veins, granting you magical control over noxious chemicals and slime, as well as a gift for changing your form to suit your needs. 

Advantages:
– Gains a +4 bonus to Saving Throws vs polymorph. 
– Is immune to disease and poison.
– Is protected from oozes. 

Disadvantages:
– May cast one fewer spell per level per day. 
~ 
