This cantrip causes a small bolt of acid to leap from the caster's hands, doing 1d5 damage to the target.~
@6037   = ~Electric Bolt~
@6038   = ~Electric Bolt

Level: 0
Range: 0
Duration: 5 rounds
Area of Effect: The caster
