This cantrip causes a small bolt of electricity to leap from the caster's hands, doing 1d5 damage to the target.~
@6039   = ~Earth Bolt~
@6040   = ~Earth Bolt

Level: 0
Range: 0
Duration: 5 rounds
Area of Effect: The caster
