@8032  = ~Rat: rats are unusually intelligent and sociable creatures, especially when enhanced by the magic of this spell. Once per 3 turns, this familiar may call upon 1d6 fellow rats to join it in combat. Rats, even domesticated ones are also no strangers to garbage and disease, and may utilize this against their enemies. Each time they successfully strike an enemy, the victim may become diseased, resulting in a short period of weakness and a 25% chance of spell failure.

