@8206  = ~Imbue Familiar

This ability can be used to imbue a familiar with the ability to cast spells. The spells are chosen from those known by the caster.  A 1st-level spell may be imbued when the caster is level 1; a 2nd-level or lower spell at level 3; a 3rd-level or lower spell at level 6; a 4th-level or lower spell at level 10, and a 5th-level or lower spell at level 15. 

